[{"time":1773796756624,"name":"eid drawing room","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, brightly lit interior scene of a luxurious living room designed in a warm, neutral color palette. A person wearing traditional festive attire (a cream kurta and an intricate gold and dark waistcoat) is seated centrally on a large, light beige upholstered sofa, smiling directly at the viewer. The background wall is cream-colored, featuring classic wainscoting paneling. High on the wall, centered above the person, is large, prominent 3D golden text in ornate Arabic script: \"[text1]\". To the upper left, near a framed artwork, is a small, subtle golden logo watermark that reads: \"[text2]\". To the left, a large window with sheer and heavy beige curtains provides bright natural light. A side table holds a table lamp and a potted plant. To the right, the sofa is adorned with various cushions, including patterned beige and dark blue\/gold ones. A side table on the right holds another lamp, books, and a small vase of flowers. In the foreground, a highly polished dark wood coffee table rests on a textured patterned area rug. On the coffee table, there is a glass of water, a bowl of dates and sweets, and a decorative golden lantern. Prominently displayed on the coffee table are large, white 3D block letters spelling out the name: \"[text3]\". The scene utilizes soft, cinematic lighting, emphasizing the luxurious textures of the fabric, wood, and metallic gold elements. Perspective is slightly low angle, capturing the full scene depth.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"3D Arabic greeting on the wall\",\"value\":\"عِيد مبارک\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Logo watermark\",\"value\":\"Imaginator AI\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"3D name text on the coffee table\",\"value\":\"Talha Usman\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773796756768.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773796756768.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773796109438,"name":"eid namaz","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, medium full-shot image showing a person of Middle Eastern or South Asian descent, centered, wearing traditional white attire (kurta and shalwar kameez). The person is smiling slightly and holding a large, vertical, aged parchment scroll with both hands in front of their chest. The person stands centered beneath a grand, symmetrical archway of a formal building, likely a mosque or shrine, constructed from smooth, polished white marble with intricate carvings and relief details. The floor is also light marble. The lighting is bright and even natural light. The vertical scroll has weathered, aged parchment texture (brown and gold tones) with decorative borders. The scroll is held open by small, dark wooden or metallic dowels at the top and bottom. Centered at the very top of the scroll, in a large, stylized calligraphy font (red and dark purple gradient): [text1]. Below the main title, centered within a small, ornate, dark blue and gold banner element: [text2]. Below the blue banner, the main body of the text is written in Urdu script (dark green\/black): [text3]. Followed by a smaller line of text: [text4]. Further down, near the bottom of the scroll: [text5]. At the very bottom center of the scroll, next to a small Facebook icon: [text6]. Style: Photorealistic, professional studio lighting, high detail, symmetrical composition, traditional, cultural announcement, Eid setting.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Main Title (Urdu calligraphy)\",\"value\":\"نماز عید الفطر\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Time\\\/Date\",\"value\":\"07:30 AM\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Name\\\/Designation line 1\",\"value\":\"حضرت مولانا معین الدین وٹو\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Name\\\/Designation line 2\",\"value\":\"دامت برکاتہم العالیہ\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Location details\",\"value\":\"بمقام : شاہی عید گاہ، منچن آباد، ضلع بہاولنگر\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Footer\\\/Branding\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773796109513.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773796109513.png","thumbSize":"385,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773795511565,"name":"wall chalking","tags":"social, post","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, cinematic image captured during the day on a street in a South Asian urban setting. The main focus is an old, textured wall constructed of reddish-brown bricks. A large rectangular area on the wall is painted bright white, serving as a freshly prepared sign board. A person, wearing light beige traditional clothing (shalwar kameez), is squatting low on the dusty ground on the left side of the frame, actively applying green paint to the sign using a brush. Scattered near the person's feet are several open cans of paint (red, blue, green, yellow) and paintbrushes. The background is blurred (shallow depth of field) showing the dusty street and partial views of motorcycles and buildings. The sign features vibrant text painted in Urdu script and Latin characters, using various colors:\n1. Top line, large font: \"[text1]\" (using blue, red, yellow, and green paint).\n2. Middle line, smaller font: \"[text2]\" (using red and green paint).\n3. Bottom left corner: \"[text3]\" (in red paint).\n4. Bottom right corner: \"[text4]\" (in dark gray paint).\nThe lighting is warm and natural, highlighting the texture of the brickwork and the fresh white paint.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Urdu text, top line, main slogan\",\"value\":\"اے آئی ڈیزائن اب امیجیٹر میں\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu text, middle line, detail\",\"value\":\"امیجیٹر میں اے آئی سے ڈیزائن اور فوٹوز بنائیں کو\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Phone number\",\"value\":\"0300 1234567\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"App name\\\/Brand name\",\"value\":\"Imagitor Al App\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773795511829.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773795511829.png","thumbSize":"512,280","type":"image"},{"time":1773795262023,"name":"eid mubarak diary","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, detailed flat lay composition of an open, cream-colored sketchbook resting on a warm brown wooden table. The notebook is centered and slightly angled. Scattered around the notebook are several colored markers (blue, green, red, black) and loose rose petals in shades of deep red and pale pink. On the open pages of the notebook: At the top, large flowing calligraphy reads '[text1]'. This text is hand-painted in a vibrant rainbow gradient (dark blue, green, yellow, orange, red). Below the calligraphy, a highly detailed, circular, ornate metallic gold frame is centered. Inside the frame is a circular illustration placeholder image of a person's portrait (head and shoulders, sketch art style). Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Below the framed placeholder, 3D rendered text sits slightly raised above the paper surface, casting soft shadows, reading '[text2]'. This text uses a layered green and blue color scheme (green on top, blue on the bottom layer). In the bottom right corner, partially on the notebook and partially on the wood, a small 3D logo and text combination appears: '[text3]'. The 'f' is the Facebook logo icon (blue square). Lighting is soft, bright studio illumination, emphasizing material textures (wood grain, paper, marker plastic). Overhead perspective with slight depth of field.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Top calligraphy greeting (Eid Mubarak)\",\"value\":\"عید مبارک\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Bottom 3D name text\",\"value\":\"حسن ضیا\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Bottom logo and attribution text\",\"value\":\"Imagitor Al\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773795262156.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773795262156.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773794474585,"name":"ice cube eid","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A hyper-realistic 3D product shot featuring a large, perfectly clear, wet ice cube or glass block centered on a white wooden plank table. Water droplets are scattered around the cube on the surface. Floating directly above the ice cube is a richly ornate, circular golden Baroque picture frame. The frame contains a circular photo placeholder. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Embossed in a frosted, light grey color onto the front face of the ice cube is the Arabic text: \"[text1]\". Below the ice cube, resting on the wooden surface, is large, volumetric Arabic text rendered in shimmering gold and dark blue reading: \"[text2]\". At the very bottom center, a small blue Facebook icon is placed next to the text: \"[text3]\". The background is heavily blurred (bokeh) with warm festive lights, garlands, and soft yellow\/orange tones, suggesting an Eid celebration atmosphere. Cinematic lighting, high reflectivity, shallow depth of field, 8K, photorealistic.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Arabic text on the ice cube (Eid Greeting)\",\"value\":\"عيد مبارك\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Large Arabic text below the cube (Name)\",\"value\":\"مُحَمَّد بن سَعْد\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Small text at the bottom (Source\\\/Brand)\",\"value\":\"Imagitor Al\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773794474693.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773794474693.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773793006537,"name":"social profile","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, cinematic close-up shot (macro perspective) of two hands holding a horizontal, transparent glass or acrylic rectangle, designed to look like a futuristic smart business card displaying a social media profile interface. The glass is perfectly clear with bright white and gold text floating on the surface. Centered at the top is a circular avatar photo placeholder with a bright golden glowing rim. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Below the avatar, the name is displayed in bold gold text: [text1], followed by a small gold checkmark icon. The next line reads: [text2]. A subsequent line features a location pin icon and the text [text3], followed by a graduation cap icon and the text [text4]. Below this, a person icon precedes the text [text5]. Statistics are centered below these lines: [text6] • [text7] • [text8]. At the bottom of the card, there are three horizontal action buttons: a vibrant blue rectangle labeled [text9], a dark gray rectangle labeled [text10], and a dark gray rectangle labeled [text11]. A small chat\/WhatsApp icon is placed to the right. The background is highly blurred (strong bokeh), showing bright, sunlit gray and silver city skyscrapers (urban environment). Bright outdoor lighting highlights the transparency and reflections on the glass.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Name\\\/Title with checkmark icon\",\"value\":\"Hakeem Farooq Soomro\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Specialization detail\",\"value\":\"Specialist in Men's Health & Infertility | Digestive Wellness\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Location text with pin icon\",\"value\":\"Minchin Abad, Pakistan\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Education text with cap icon\",\"value\":\"Tibbia College Lahore\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Owner information with person icon\",\"value\":\"Owner: Ibn Sina Herbals\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Followers count\",\"value\":\"10k followers\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Following count\",\"value\":\"0 following\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Posts count\",\"value\":\"4.0k posts\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Blue button text\",\"value\":\"Follow\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"},{\"label\":\"Dark button text\",\"value\":\"Message\",\"key\":\"[text10]\"},{\"label\":\"Dark button text\",\"value\":\"Call\",\"key\":\"[text11]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773793006627.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773793006627.png","thumbSize":"505,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773792844680,"name":"eid profile","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A circular, ornate, photorealistic greeting graphic with a rich, dark gold and emerald green theme, designed for Eid al-Fitr celebration. The scene is framed by a complex, thick circular border made of polished gold bands, set against a dark brown\/black background with subtle golden Islamic patterns. In the center, dominating the middle ground, is a photorealistic depiction of the Green Dome (Masjid Nabawi) and its associated architecture (minarets visible behind the dome), set against a light, diffused sky background. To the left, several highly detailed, antique golden Islamic lanterns (fanous) hang down, emitting warm, glowing light and subtle particle effects. To the right of the dome, there is a photorealistic vertical portrait placeholder of an individual wearing a white kurta and a black kufi cap, facing forward and smiling. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. The Urdu text \"[text1]\" is curved across the top inside the gold circle border, rendered in polished gold, 3D script. The large Urdu text \"[text2]\" is centered below the dome, rendered in massive, reflective, 3D polished gold script with deep shadows. The Urdu text \"[text3]\" is placed below the large text, rendered in a smaller, flat gold script. A small horizontal banner at the very bottom contains a blue Facebook icon and the white text \"[text4]\". Cinematic, dramatic lighting, high gloss metallic gold texture.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Urdu text, top curved\",\"value\":\"تمام عالم اسلام کو\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu text, large center\",\"value\":\"عید الفطر\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu text, bottom center\",\"value\":\"دل سے مبارک ہو\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Logo text, bottom banner\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773792844776.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773792844776.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786749542,"name":"eid namaz times","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A highly detailed digital illustration designed as an event poster, featuring a photorealistic style with natural daylighting. The scene is set outdoors against a smooth, light beige\/white stucco wall under a bright blue sky with subtle clouds. To the right, a large white ornate archway or gateway of Islamic architecture is visible.\n\n**Layout and Objects:**\n1.  **Upper Area:** A string of colorful pennant flags (green, yellow, red, blue) with crescent and star emblems hangs along the top edge of the wall.\n2.  **Right Side:** A person wearing traditional white Islamic attire (Shalwar Kameez and Taqiyah\/cap) stands smiling, holding a paintbrush and an artist's palette, indicating they are painting the wall. A paint can and brushes are on the ground near their feet. Behind this person, a mural is painted on the wall depicting the Kaaba and the green dome and minarets of Al-Masjid an-Nabawi against a dark blue, starry background.\n3.  **Left Side:** An arrangement of vibrant flowers (roses in red, pink, yellow) and green foliage surrounds an open Holy Book (Quran) resting on a wooden stand (rehal). Two ornate gold\/bronze hanging lanterns flank the book and flowers.\n\n**Typography and Text Placement:**\n*   In the upper left corner, small text reads: '[text1]'.\n*   The main title, '[text2]', is centrally placed in large, flowing Arabic\/Urdu script, dark brown\/black with a thick golden outline.\n*   Below the title, the text '[text3]' is placed within a decorative horizontal dark blue banner with gold borders and a sparkling stars motif.\n*   Below the banner, the text '[text4]' is centered in brown script.\n*   Below that, smaller text reads: '[text5]'.\n*   Lower center, two lines of location text are placed: '[text6]' followed by '[text7]'.\n*   In the bottom right corner, a small blue Facebook icon is placed next to the logo text '[text8]'.\n\n**Style:** High-resolution digital painting, detailed textures simulating stucco, fabric, and realistic florals. Bright, even lighting. Illustration quality.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Corner number\\\/identifier\",\"value\":\"٥٠٧٥\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Title (Eid Prayer Name)\",\"value\":\"نماز عيد الفطر\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Time\",\"value\":\"07:30 AM\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Name Line 1\",\"value\":\"حضرت مولانا معین الدین وٹو\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Name Line 2 (Dua)\",\"value\":\"دامت برکاتہم العالیہ\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Location Line 1\",\"value\":\"شاہی عید گاہ، منچن آباد،\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Location Line 2\",\"value\":\"بمقام : ضلع بہاولنگر\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Logo\\\/Footer text\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786749668.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786749668.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786651168,"name":"eid namaz times","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic vertical flyer\/poster design for an event announcement. The background is a high-quality photograph featuring ornate Islamic architecture, specifically a large, recessed arched doorway (Iwan) covered in intricate, colorful mosaic tiles (predominantly blues, greens, yellows, and earthy tones). Several large decorative ceramic pots holding vibrant yellow\/orange flowers (marigolds) and green palm foliage are placed symmetrically on the tiled ground flanking the arch.\nCentered in the foreground, filling the lower half of the composition, is a full-length photo placeholder of a smiling person wearing a traditional white garment and a white cap. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible.\nThe lighting is bright, natural outdoor illumination, creating realistic textures and depth.\n\nText Overlays (Arabic and English):\n1. Upper center, arching over the doorway, is the large, stylized Arabic text: \"[text1]\". The text is white with a thick white outline and dark drop shadows, rendered in elegant calligraphy.\n2. Directly below the main title, centered, is the text \"[text2]\" rendered in white, set within a small, dark blue, pointed horizontal banner.\n3. Below the time banner, spanning the width of the arch, is a large, ornate teal\/dark green, horizontal banner with gold trim and curved edges. This banner contains two lines of white Arabic text. The primary line is: \"[text3]\".\n4. The secondary, smaller line of text immediately below the primary name on the teal banner is: \"[text4]\".\n5. Below the teal banner, centered and overlapping the upper body of the person slightly, is the location text: \"[text5]\". This text is rendered in a deep orange\/brown color.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Main title, Arabic script (Prayer name)\",\"value\":\"نماز عید الفطر\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Time\\\/Date\",\"value\":\"07:30 AM\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Name line 1 (Arabic)\",\"value\":\"حضرت مولانا معین الدین وٹو\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Name line 2 (Arabic blessing)\",\"value\":\"دامت برکاتہم العالیہ\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Location details (Arabic)\",\"value\":\"بمقام : شاہی عیدگاه، منچن آباد، ضلع بہاولنگر\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786651245.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786651245.png","thumbSize":"336,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786589791,"name":"eid acrylic design","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic 3D rendered vertical greeting card design with an ornate, rich dark brown and bronze monochromatic theme, resembling deep relief carving on wood or metal. The entire composition is framed by an intricate, repeating geometric and floral Islamic decorative border, rendered in polished bronze with deep shadows. The background surface is matte dark brown. Centered top-left, the phrase \"[text1]\" is carved in dark bronze. Below this, the bold text \"[text2]\" is prominently featured. Below the English text, the connecting phrase \"[text3]\" is carved in a smaller size. Dominating the left center is massive, highly detailed 3D Arabic calligraphy reading \"[text4]\", rendered in embossed dark bronze material with realistic depth and hard shadows. On the right center, balancing the calligraphy, is a large circular photo frame with an ornate carved border. This frame contains a sepia-toned portrait photo placeholder of a smiling person (upper body shot). Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. At the bottom right, beneath the circular frame, a decorative shield shape is carved out. Inside this shield, the text \"[text5]\" is centered above the smaller subtitle \"[text6]\". Cinematic, dramatic lighting enhances the 3D texture and depth of the carving.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top connecting phrase (Urdu\\\/Arabic)\",\"value\":\"تمام اہل اسلام کو\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Company Name\",\"value\":\"BooleanBites Ltd\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Connecting phrase below company name\",\"value\":\"کی طرف سے عید الفطر مبارک\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Large Calligraphy (Eid Al-Fitr Mubarak)\",\"value\":\"عید الفطر مبارک\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom logo main text\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Bottom logo subtitle text\",\"value\":\"Graphic Design app\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786589873.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786589873.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786544410,"name":"eid billboard","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A highly photorealistic, sunlit outdoor medium shot featuring a rectangular roadside billboard sign mounted on a dark grey pole. The background shows blurred green trees and sunlight, with a paved asphalt road and concrete sidewalk visible below. The sign displays intricate, saturated, multicolored floral\/Mughal decorative borders (red, green, gold, blue), framing a central cream-colored panel. Centered in the top half of the panel is large red and gold Arabic calligraphy reading: '[text1]'. Below this is the English text '[text2]'. At the bottom center of the panel, aligned horizontally, are two pieces of contact information: '[text3]' preceded by a green WhatsApp icon, and '[text4]' preceded by a blue Facebook icon. Below the sign, standing next to the pole on the sidewalk, is a person dressed in a dark maroon shalwar kameez and black waistcoat. The person is smiling and looking towards the camera. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. The lighting is soft, natural, golden hour light, with a shallow depth of field focusing sharply on the sign and the person.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Arabic Greeting\",\"value\":\"عید سعیدالمبارک\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Name on Sign\",\"value\":\"Ahmed bin Saud\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Phone Number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Social Handle\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786544470.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786544470.png","thumbSize":"286,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786495592,"name":"eid profile gold","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, highly detailed portrait composition suitable for an Eid greeting. The scene features a warm, pastel-colored sunset sky background with soft, radial light rays emanating from the upper area. In the center is a large, ornate circular frame made of polished, intricately carved gold with Islamic geometric patterns and scrollwork. The gold frame has a high shine and dramatic lighting, casting soft shadows. A central circular photo placeholder of an individual is embedded within the frame, focused and well-lit. Below the photo placeholder, integrated into the bottom of the circular frame, is a creamy white, semicircular\/crescent plaque bordered by gold trim. This plaque holds the text. Above the plaque, in 3D gold Arabic calligraphy, is the text \"[text1]\". Centered on the plaque in a serif font is \"[text2]\". Below this text, aligned left, is a small WhatsApp icon followed by the number \"[text3]\". Below that, aligned left, is a small Facebook icon followed by the text \"[text4]\". Faintly visible in the distant background, within the frame, is the silhouette of a minaret and a few flying birds. Cinematic lighting, professional photography quality, 8K resolution. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Arabic Greeting\",\"value\":\"عِيدُكُمْ سَعِيدٌ الْمُبَارَك\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Name\",\"value\":\"Ahmed bin Saud\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Phone Number\",\"value\":\"0300-1234567\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Facebook Handle\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786495655.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786495655.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786436550,"name":"eid wood design","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, highly detailed 3D relief carving into dark, polished walnut wood. The carving is square and framed by an intricate, thick wooden border with multiple layers of ornamental molding. The background of the panel features deep bas-relief patterns of geometric and floral Islamic arabesque designs (mashrabiya). The composition features large, ornate Arabic\/Urdu calligraphy in a strong Naskh or Thuluth style, deeply carved into the wood surface. At the top edge, carved in a relatively smaller, horizontal line: \"[text1]\". Below this, centered, slightly smaller text flanked by a star on the right and a crescent moon and star motif on the left: \"[text2]\". Dominating the left and center is the largest, stylized calligraphy: \"[text3]\" above \"[text4]\". To the right of the large calligraphy, centered vertically, is a deeply recessed circular wooden frame. Inside this frame is a photorealistic placeholder of a person, depicted from the chest up, arms crossed, wearing a traditional brown, embroidered tunic (sherwani or kurta) that harmonizes in color with the wood. The figure is integrated seamlessly into the carving, appearing like a highly detailed relief sculpture or a photograph rendered with wood-like texture. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. At the bottom center, a horizontal, decorative wooden cartouche contains the name: \"[text5]\". The cartouche has flanking carved decorative elements (vines\/leaves). Dramatic, cinematic lighting (Chiaroscuro) casting deep, sharp shadows to emphasize the three-dimensional depth and texture of the wood grain and the complexity of the carving. Rich, warm mahogany and walnut color palette. Ultra-high detail, professional photography quality.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top Greeting Line\",\"value\":\"عید الفطر مبارک۔ تمام اہل اسلام کو\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Traditional Arabic Supplication\",\"value\":\"تقبل الله منا ومنكم\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Title Part 1\",\"value\":\"عید الفطر\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Main Title Part 2\",\"value\":\"مبارک\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Signature Name\",\"value\":\"عبدالرحمان\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786436637.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786436637.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786389708,"name":"eid festive","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic graphic design for an Eid Al-Fitr greeting card. The background is a rich, deep emerald green with a subtle teal gradient, illuminated by dramatic cinematic lighting. The upper section features a stylized silhouette of a mosque (domes and minarets) under a bright golden crescent moon and star. The scene is decorated with intricate golden Islamic geometric trelliswork framing the corners and several hanging illuminated golden Arabic lanterns (fanoos). The entire image is dusted with glowing golden bokeh effects. A large circular photo placeholder is positioned on the right side, featuring a smiling person wearing a dark suit and light grey tie. This circular placeholder is emphasized by a thick, radiant golden glow. The text is stacked on the left side in elegant Arabic\/Urdu script (Nasta'liq style). The text arrangement is: Top left, \"[text1]\" in gold; followed by \"[text2]\" in white; then the large focal text \"[text3]\" in bold gold; followed by \"[text4]\" in white. At the bottom center, in smaller white script: \"[text5]\". Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Highly detailed, festive, ultra quality.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Arabic Greeting\",\"value\":\"تقبل الله منا و منكم\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu phrase (To the entire Islamic world)\",\"value\":\"تمام عالم اسلام کو\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Occasion Name (Eid al-Fitr)\",\"value\":\"عید الفطر\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Urdu Blessing (Very Happy)\",\"value\":\"بہت مبارک ہو ۔\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Sender Name (From: Talha bin Ali)\",\"value\":\"منجانب: طلحہ بن علی\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786389779.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786389779.png","thumbSize":"512,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786306649,"name":"eid night wall","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, cinematic vertical shot capturing a festive Eid greeting scene at night. The background features a dark, textured brick wall illuminated by warm light. On the left side, a placeholder (a person wearing white traditional South Asian attire and brown sandals, leaning against the brick wall) is positioned centrally. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. To the right of the person, dominating the mid-ground, is a large, ornate 3D golden relief decoration. This decoration features a detailed silhouette of a mosque structure rising above a large, intricately patterned crescent moon. Above the crescent, the large golden Arabic calligraphy reads: [text1]. Below this, smaller golden Arabic text reads: [text2]. Hanging from the top edge, three intricate, glowing golden lanterns cast strong, warm, orange light onto the scene and the brick wall, creating dramatic shadows and highlights. Below the person's right foot, near the bottom right corner, two glowing social media icons (Facebook blue and Instagram gradient) are placed vertically, each followed by the text: [text3] and [text4]. The ground is a dark paved surface. Cinematic lighting, deep shadows, and high contrast.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Large Arabic Eid greeting text\",\"value\":\"عید مبارک\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Small Arabic blessing text\",\"value\":\"تقبل الله منا ومنكم\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Social Media Handle (Facebook)\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Social Media Handle (Instagram)\",\"value\":\"Imagitor AI\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786306702.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786306702.png","thumbSize":"276,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786243340,"name":"eid night","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, high-quality, cinematic vertical greeting card design for Eid. The scene is set at night under a dark teal and deep green sky. The background features the silhouette of a grand Islamic mosque complex with multiple domes and tall minarets, warmly illuminated by golden internal lights. A bright crescent moon is visible in the upper right quadrant. The entire composition is framed by a decorative archway, with string lights (fairy lights) hanging along the top border. Ornate Islamic lanterns (Fanoos) are prominent in the foreground and sides, casting strong, warm orange light and creating intense bokeh effects across the image. A central vertical photo placeholder features a person, smiling and dressed in a traditional cream\/off-white silk kurta with intricate gold embroidery around the neck. The lighting is dramatic and warm. Large calligraphy text \"[text1]\" in luxurious gold is centered at the top. Below this, aligned right (Urdu\/Arabic reading direction) in smaller white text, are two lines: \"[text2]\" followed by \"[text3]\". Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible.","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Large gold calligraphy Eid greeting\",\"value\":\"عید مبارک\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Smaller white text line 1\",\"value\":\"میری طرف سے تمام مسلمانوں کو خوشیوں بھری\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Smaller white text line 2\",\"value\":\"عید مبارک\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786243402.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786243402.png","thumbSize":"412,512","type":"image"},{"time":1773786172572,"name":"eid card","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, cinematic image of a highly ornate, textured Eid al-Fitr greeting card standing upright on a reflective white marble surface. The scene is set in a luxurious, sunlit interior with a shallow depth of field, featuring opulent golden-trimmed furniture and silk curtains blurred in the background. The card itself is light gold\/beige, with embossed arabesque patterns covering the surface. The edges of the card are slightly rough and decorative. All Arabic\/Urdu text is rendered in thick, glowing, 3D reflective gold calligraphy. Text placement: Top center in smaller script: '[text1]'. Large, central text is '[text2]'. Below the main text: 'اہل اسلام کو عید الفطر مبارك'. In the bottom right corner: '[text4]'. Design elements include an antique, intricate brass Moroccan lantern hanging near the center right, emitting warm, colorful light (red, green, amber). A small silver plate holding colorful traditional Arabic sweets (ma'amoul, baklava) rests on the bottom left corner of the card, next to a golden crescent moon decoration. Lighting is dramatic, with strong, warm sunlight streaming from the upper left, creating brilliant highlights on the gold accents and soft shadows on the table. Highly detailed, high resolution.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Top Arabic blessing text\",\"value\":\"تقبل الله منا ومنكم صالح الأعمال\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Main central greeting text\",\"value\":\"عيد الفطر مبارك\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"Secondary smaller greeting text\",\"value\":\"اہل اسلام کو عید الفطر مبارک\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Signature\\\/Name\",\"value\":\"على احمد\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786172637.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786172637.png","thumbSize":"512,280","type":"image"},{"time":1773786118105,"name":"eid glass","tags":"eid","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A photorealistic, ultra-high definition image capturing a transparent, rectangular holographic glass card held horizontally by two hands against a deeply blurred, vibrant flower garden background (strong bokeh effect featuring pink, white, and yellow flowers). The scene is illuminated by warm, strong backlighting creating cinematic lens flares and golden highlights. The transparent card displays digital text and elements in a reflective golden color. Centered at the top is a circular photo placeholder with a bright golden glowing border and a small golden checkmark icon positioned outside its top right edge. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. Below the photo placeholder, the text \"[text1]\" is displayed in gold Urdu\/Arabic script. Directly below this, large stylized gold calligraphy reads \"[text2]\". Further down, a smaller gold text phrase reads \"[text3]\". At the bottom of the card, three horizontal, rounded rectangular buttons with glossy gold metallic texture are positioned: the left button reads \"[text4]\", the middle button reads \"[text5]\", and the right button reads \"[text6]\".","entities":"[{\"key\":\"[text1]\",\"label\":\"Name below avatar\",\"value\":\"بہروز عادل سومرو\"},{\"key\":\"[text2]\",\"label\":\"Calligraphy greeting\",\"value\":\"عید مبارک\"},{\"key\":\"[text3]\",\"label\":\"Extended greeting phrase\",\"value\":\"اہل اسلام کو خوشیوں بھری عید مبارک\"},{\"key\":\"[text4]\",\"label\":\"Left button text\",\"value\":\"تشکر\"},{\"key\":\"[text5]\",\"label\":\"Middle button text\",\"value\":\"صدقہ\"},{\"key\":\"[text6]\",\"label\":\"Right button text\",\"value\":\"خوشیاں\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1773786118189.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1773786118189.png","thumbSize":"504,512","type":"image"}]